thread.title: BRIEF-Sharjah Islamic Bank Q1 Profit Rises

title: BRIEF-Sharjah Islamic Bank Q1 Profit Rises

organizations.name: brief-sharjah islamic bank q1 profit rises reuters

text:
April 29, 2018 / 10:58 AM / a few seconds ago BRIEF-Sharjah Islamic Bank Q1 Profit Rises Reuters Staff
April 29 (Reuters) - SHARJAH ISLAMIC BANK:
* Q1 NET PROFIT 143.1 MILLION DIRHAMS VERSUS 139.1 MILLION DIRHAMS YEAR AGO
* Q1 NET OPERATING INCOME 254.8 MILLION DIRHAMS VERSUS 237.8 MILLION DIRHAMS YEAR AGO
* AS OF END-MARCH 2018, CUSTOMER DEPOSITS STAND AT 25.47 BILLION DIRHAMS
* Q1 TOTAL INCOME 400.6 MILLION DIRHAMS VERSUS 366.2 MILLION DIRHAMS YEAR AGO Source:( bit.ly/2r86cdT ) Further company coverage:
